{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Your Mac app already contains a wealth of accessibility information just waiting to be reported through the NSAccessibility APIs. Doing so opens your app up to growing numbers of VoiceOver users and gives you and your users a way to automate your application’s interface. Come learn about design patterns that simply the process of making your application and custom views accessible, and discover accessibility enhancements in Lion."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-127-Design-Patterns-to-Simplify-Mac-Accessibility","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/127\/","type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"}},"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Design Patterns to Simplify Mac Accessibility","roleHeading":"WWDC11"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-127-design-patterns-to-simplify-mac-accessibility"]}],"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","images":[{